ice spokesperson, Tee Leo lkoro confirmed the ugly incident. Ikoro disputed that the suspect is an Hausa man but that he’s from Benue state. He added that the police detectives have been able to extract information from the suspect because he’s still unconscious after the severe beating he received from the youths who caught him in the act. The police image maker added that the family of the victim have not informed the police of the incident. Vanguard News Nigeria NO doubt about it, they were still amateur in the illicit game of armed robbery. Two brothers ,Olubunmi Ojo and Adekunle Ojo who were paraded alongside 27 other criminals by the Ondo Police Command were just learning the rope and according to them this was their first outing. South West… March 5, 2015 In "News" A 50-year-old father of two, Kamoru Sumaila, has been arrested for allegedly raping a 10-year-old girl in Akure, the Ondo State capital. Vanguard gathered that the suspected rapist was arrested by officials of the Nigeria Security and Civil Defence Corps, NSCDC in the state. November 29, 2020 In "Metro" AKURE — NO doubt the sex romp by the students of both Adeyemi College of Education, Ondo city and Rufus Giwa Polytechnic, Owo, in Ondo State and a barber was a well planned script. The  barber, who is also a friend to the lover boy, Vanguard, gathered, was involved in… August 11, 2017 In "Crime Guard"